post_text:
Please see our new Start Here - Remote Learning page on our website! This contains step by step instructions for you to make sure you're ready for the new school year. There are supplemental instructions, videos, and information to help you prepare for remote learning. Learn about ParentSquare (make sure you register), Teams, and resources available. Link: https://www.arbor145.org/Content2/starthere

Thank you and have a good weekend!
Arbor Park
